Teso South MP Mary Emaase has warned politicians not to threaten her supporters.She said frequent warnings have been sent ti her supporters telling them not to back her and the Jubilee party. Emaase is among the campaign team in Western championing for President Uhuru Kenyatta&rsquo;s reelection.&ldquo;Everyone has a right to choose their favourite candidate. Jubilee is just like any other party. Who said that ODM or any other party is special?&rdquo; she asked.She said she will forwards such cases to ensure they are reported to police.Emaase spoke on Monday at Adungosi trading centre, Teso South.